.TH manta-power 1  "power " 
.SH NAME
manta\-power \- Manage node and cluster power state
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmanta power\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage node and cluster power state
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
manta\-power\-on(1)
Power on nodes or a cluster
.TP
manta\-power\-off(1)
Power off nodes or a cluster
.TP
manta\-power\-reset(1)
Reset (reboot) nodes or a cluster
